text.section:
Except as permitted by this section or in accordance with a permit obtained from the Administration, a person may not:
Make an opening in any State highway;
Place any structure on any State highway;
Change or renew any structure placed on any State highway;
Dig up any State highway for any purpose, including the placement of pipes, sewers, poles, wires, or rails;
Plant or remove any tree on any State highway; or
Place any obstruction or improvement on any State highway.
